        </item>
        <item>
            <title>AMD Ryzen 7 9800X3D 烧毁事件，YouTuber 原价收购研究</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/15/ryzen-7-burn-issue/wireless-home/desktop-pc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ryzen-7-burn-issue</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/15/ryzen-7-burn-issue/wireless-home/desktop-pc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 15:00:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[桌上电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AMD]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AMD Ryzen 7]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AMD Ryzen 7 9800X3D]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Ryzen 7 9800X3D]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1275380</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>AMD 早前推出的 Ryzen 7 9800X3D 晶片比喻为当代最强游戏晶片，但近日一名 Reddit 用户表示其 AMD Ryzen 7 9800X3D 处理器安装在 X870 主机板后无法启动，最后更过热烧毁。事件引起 PC 硬件技术 YouTube 频道 Gamers Nexus 关注，并表示会原价收购涉事 CPU 研究。</p><blockquote class="reddit-embed-bq" style="height: 500px;" data-embed-height="240"><p><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/pcmasterrace/comments/1gqaryi/new_9800x3d_msi_tomahawk_x870_burned_up_i_guess/">New 9800x3d + MSI Tomahawk X870 burned up? I guess that&#8217;s why it wouldn&#8217;t POST</a><br />
by<a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/TrumpPooPoosPants/">u/TrumpPooPoosPants</a> in<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/pcmasterrace/">pcmasterrace</a></p></blockquote><p><script async="" src="https://embed.reddit.com/widgets.js" charset="UTF-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275382" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/remyign-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/remyign-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/remyign-scaled.jpeg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275386" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mnqb6wq-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mnqb6wq-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mnqb6wq-scaled.jpeg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275387" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z8zlb9z-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z8zlb9z-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z8zlb9z-scaled.jpeg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲TrumpPooPooPants 展示烧毁的 AMD CPU<br />
图片来源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/TrumpPooPoosPants/">TrumpPooPoosPants@Reddit</a></p><p>根据 TrumpPooPoosPants 描述，他砌机后发现电脑无法开机，检查时发现处理器及 AM5 插槽有部分针脚已经烧毁。据《PC GamesN》报道，现时不能完全排除 AMD CPU 制造时有缺陷，但有其他几位 Reddit 用户指插槽周围的塑胶严重损坏，CPU 部分针脚出现弯曲情况，怀疑 CPU 被稍微弯曲甚至反转插入插槽，质疑 TrumpPooPoosPants 安装不当引致火警。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275385" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241115175046-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241115175046-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241115175046.jpg 820w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲网友指部分针脚屈曲，令 CPU 无法正确安装</p><p>PC 硬件技术 YouTube 频道 Gamers Nexus 提出以原价收购烧坏 CPU 作研究之用，TrumpPooPoosPants 欣然接受其建议，估计其后 Gamers Nexus 会公布分析结果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275389" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241115182049-694x300.png" alt="" width="694" height="300" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241115182049-694x300.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241115182049.png 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://videocardz.com/newz/amd-ryzen-7-9800x3d-burns-out-for-unlucky-redditor-socket-defect-or-user-error-suspected">Video Cardz</a>、<a href="https://www.tomshardware.com/pc-components/cpus/two-ryzen-7-9800x3d-cpus-burned-out-on-x870-motherboards-vendor-investigates-the-ryzen-burnout-issues">Tom&#8217;s Hardware</a>、<a href="https://www.pcgamesn.com/amd/ryzen-7-9800x3d-burn-out">PC GamesN</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
